## If Your Password Has Special Characters:

If your MongoDB password contains:
- `@` → use `%40`
- `#` → use `%23`
- `$` → use `%24`
- `&` → use `%26`
- `%` → use `%25`

For example, if password is `Pass@123#`, use:
```
mongodb+srv://touristadmin:Pass%40123%23@codinghub...